OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sat 27 Jun to Mon 6 Jul
OL,6,FFairly changeable conditions at first
OL,7,Fwith periods of rain and showers, and
OL,8,Fthere could be some thundery outbreaks
OL,9,Fat times. There will likely be some
OL,10,Fdrier and brighter spells though. Into
OL,11,FJuly changeable conditions are likely
OL,12,Fto continue as Atlantic lows move in
OL,13,Ffrom the west, but with transient
OL,14,Fperiods of high pressure. This will
OL,15,Flead to spells of rain and cloud
OL,16,Finterspersed with more settled
OL,17,Fperiods. Temperatures remain widely
OL,18,Fabove average, and the far southeast
OL,19,Fmay retain some of the hot
OL,20,Ftemperatures at first, but likely
OL,21,Fcooler than the preceding few days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
